st Jump: What Made Him Finally Quit? What Are the Most Insanely Daring Stunts Since Evel Knievel? 7 of History's Most Fearless Female Daredevils Secretariat The Olympic Games Winter Olympics Technology Kentucky Derby Flashback: Soap Box Derby Mania The Dictators The Nearly Men The Meltdown The Icon The Rout Loading… See More Ad Choices Advertise Closed Captioning Copyright Policy Corporate Information Employment Opportunities FAQ/Contact Us Privacy Notice Terms of Use TV Parental Guidelines RSS Feeds Accessibility Support © 2020 A&E Television Networks, LLC. All Rights Reserved.